Designated a world cultural heritage festival by UNESCO and added to the Representative List of the Intangible Cultural Heritage of Humanity in 2009; its origins can be traced back to 2000 BC yet its spirit of reason, progress, knowledge and brotherhood remains relevant and extensive to this day. » more...
